nodes.text: Brian Dobson (born September 9, 1973) is an English-Canadian voice actor who provided the voice of Jek-14 in LEGO Star Wars: The Yoda Chronicles and LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures. He is the younger brother of Michael and Paul Dobson.
